title: Unemployment rate in Brunei Darussalam 2019
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Unemployment rate. In total the number of data points it has is 21.
Overall Unemployment rate has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2015 and 2016.
Maximum Unemployment rate, about 9.32 was reported at Year 2017
Minimum Unemployment rate about 5.57 was reached at Year 1999
